Adding Year Slicer 16

Adding Year Slicer 




1.From the Visualization pane, click on Slicer and Drag ‘Year’ column from Power Plant table to the Values field of Slice
2.In the Format Pane on the right, Go to General => Properties and enter the values below for formatting
General=>
Height = 108
Width = 215
Position =>
Horizontal = 0
Vertical = 81
Title => on
Title->Text = Year
Font = Segoe UI Bold, Size = 12
Text Color = #FFFFFF
Background Color = #17866c
Horizontal Alignment -> Center
Effects=>
Background = On
Color = #ECF5F3
Transparency = 0%
Visual =>
Style -> Slicer Setting -> Between
Slicer Header -> OFF
Values =>
Font = Segoe UI Bold – 9
Font Color = #000000
Slider = On
